OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FBreezy start with a mixture
OL,6,Fof sunny spells and showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy. Winds will ease
OL,8,Fthrough the day, with showers also
OL,9,Ffading into the evening. Feeling warm
OL,10,Fin any sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOften
OL,13,Fcloudy Friday, with the odd shower,
OL,14,Fbut also some brighter spells. Rain
OL,15,Flikely Saturday morning, clearing to
OL,16,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier, and
OL,17,Fsunnier Sunday with winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
